Physical interpretation of such singular behavior is not clear to
us, so we shall primarily concentrate our consideration on the
early evolution before hitting the critical time, 
. As the total energy ought to be conserved, a
plausible possibility suggested in is that the
missing energy has escaped through the singularity to form an
array of codimension-one D-branes. We leave viability of this
scenario aside for future study. (See section 5 for further
discussion.)


